<br>
I went to GFay and took off my noodle. I cast it (MoR) on an orc pawn. I hand to hand hit him until he died.  This spell does not add damge to your blows or I would have noticed that my hand to hand hits of 2 and 3 where hitting for 8 or 9 (which would kill an orc pawn in 3 hits or so).<br>
<br>
Its easy to test if you use on lowbie mobs with 20 or 30 hps.<br>
<br>
Its currently doing nothing but generating agro.<br>
